statement: select yr,  count(distinct[skew] lo_orderkey) from (select yr, case when (yr >= 1992 and yr <=1997) then (lo_orderkey%10) else lo_orderkey end as lo_orderkey from  (select year(lo_commitdate) as yr, murmur_hash3_32(lo_orderkey) as lo_orderkey, lo_extendedprice from lineorder_flat) t2 left outer join[shuffle]  (select column_0 as c0 from (values(1))t0)t1 on t1.c0 = t2.lo_extendedprice ) t group by yr;
